text: Abdesselem Regragui (born 1939) is a Moroccan gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Moroccan male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Morocco Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rabat
